1797	[super] Webstore v2 - Integrated and based on ElasticSearch	rgrp	rgrp	"Etherpad: http://ckan.okfnpad.org/webstore

== Questions ==
 1. Authorization (and url structure)
    * Authorization API?
 2. How do we integrate webstore into main site
   * /dataset/{xyz}/resource/{r-id}/data => /api/rest/dataset/{xyz}/resource/{r-id}/data
   * /dataset/{xyz}/resource/{r-id}/raw <= raw / bulk version of this data ...
 3. What query API do we use 
  * We just use elasticsearch
  * https://github.com/okfn/recline/issues/34

== Details ==

Layout on ES:

{{{
elasticsearch/{index}/{type-id}

index = ckan-{ckan-id}
type-id = resource-id (1)
}}}

Request path:

Req => Nginx => CKAN App (authz) => req to elasticsearch and returns results

See as an example: https://github.com/okfn/elastic-proxy"	enhancement	new	critical	ckan-v1.7	ckan				ckan	none
